file.name: testExamples.yml
file.content:
---
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Corunet Challenge Game Server
  description: Test File for SCC MultiApi Plugin.
  contact:
    name: Corunet
    url: coru.net
    email: info@coru.net
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
- url: http://localhost:8080/v1
paths:
  /games/{gameId}:
    get:
      summary: Info for a specific game
      operationId: showGameById
      description: Test File for SCC MultiApi Plugin.
      tags:
      - games
      parameters:
      - name: gameId
        in: path
        required: true
        description: The id of the game to retrieve
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          example: 1
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/GameInfo"
components:
  schemas:
    GameInfo:
      type: object
      required:
      - gameName
      - rooms
      properties:
        rooms:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          example: 1
        gameName:
          type: string
          example: hangman
tags:
- name: games
  description: Test description for SCC MultiApi Plugin.
